## Anti-Pattern'ler
| Anti-Pattern | Dogru Yaklasim |
|---|---|
| `FROM latest` | Pinned version tag |
| Root user container | Non-root USER |
| Secret in ENV/Dockerfile | Key Vault / sealed secrets |
| COPY . . son stage | COPY --from=build specific files |
| Monolithic CI pipeline | Parallel jobs + caching |
| Log string interpolation | Structured logging |
| Alert fatigue | Actionable alerts only (SLO-based) |
